comment: Gallinari (DEN) legally contests Davis' (NOP) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hill (NOP) makes contact with Jokic (DEN) that affects his SQBR.
Davis (NOP) makes marginal contact with Gallinari (DEN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Davis (NOP) is not in a legal guarding position and makes contact with Gallinari (DEN) that affects his shot attempt.
Davis (NOP) sets the screen on Harris (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Moore (NOP) on the screen that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Hill (NOP) makes incidental contact with Jokic (DEN) during rebounding.
Hill (NOP) maintains legal guarding position and deflects the ball away from Gallinari (DEN).
Gallinari (DEN) does not advance the ball from the backcourt into his own frontcourt during the allowed 8 seconds.
Cousins (NOP) makes contact with Jokic (DEN) that affects his SQBR.
DEN is awarded a timeout within 5 seconds.
Moore (NOP) makes incidental contact with Murray (DEN) that does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
Cousins (NOP) makes marginal contact with Chandler (DEN) on the perimeter.
Cousins (NOP) makes contact to the body of Chandler (DEN) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holiday (NOP) loses possession of the ball in the front court and retrieves it in the back court.
Hill (NOP) commits a take foul on Mudiay (DEN).
Harris (DEN) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
Cousins (NOP) makes contact with Harris (DEN) that affects his FOM.
Harris (DEN) maintains legal guarding position defending Holiday (NOP).
